---
import SectionWrapper from '../SectionWrapper.astro';
import GlassCard from '../GlassCard.astro';
import Cursor from '../Cursor.astro';
---
<div class="guide-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<SectionWrapper bg="base" id="about" class="guide-section">
  <!-- Section label -->
  <p class="section-label">// 03 ABOUT</p>

  <!-- Two-column layout -->
  <div class="guide-grid">
    <!-- LEFT column: empathy copy -->
    <div class="empathy-col">
      <p class="empathy-opener">
        You've already tried the obvious answers.
      </p>

      <div class="empathy-body">
        <p>
          The template site from the platform everyone recommended. The freelancer
          who promised a two-week redesign. The agency that showed you a beautiful
          deck and disappeared after launch. The app that was going to sync
          everything. The AI tool you signed up for, used twice, and now pay for
          every month anyway.
        </p>

        <p>
          None of it worked because none of it started with a diagnosis. Someone
          sold you a solution before asking what was actually broken.
        </p>

        <p>
          Maximum Execution is a diagnostic-first development practice based in
          Richmond, Virginia. Every project starts the same way: map the systems,
          identify the specific failure points, and write a problem statement you
          can read, verify, and agree on before a single line of code gets touched.
          One person does all of it — no handoffs, no committees, no account
          managers between you and the work.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT column: authority + testimonials -->
    <div class="proof-col">
      <!-- Authority terminal -->
      <GlassCard class="authority-card">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <span class="dot g"></span>
          <span class="terminal-label">max.exe // authority log</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-rule"></div>
        <div class="status-list">
          <div class="status-line">
            <span class="status-badge ok">[OK]</span>
            <span class="status-text">Projects shipped:</span>
            <span class="status-value">12+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="status-line">
            <span class="status-badge ok">[OK]</span>
            <span class="status-text">Deadlines missed:</span>
            <span class="status-value">0</span>
          </div>
          <div class="status-line">
            <span class="status-badge ok">[OK]</span>
            <span class="status-text">Code ownership at delivery:</span>
            <span class="status-value">100%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="status-line">
            <span class="status-badge ok">[OK]</span>
            <span class="status-text">Avg response time:</span>
            <span class="status-value">&lt; 24hr</span>
          </div>
          <div class="status-line">
            <span class="status-badge ok">[OK]</span>
            <span class="status-text">Problems diagnosed first:</span>
            <span class="status-value">every single one</span>
          </div>
          <div class="status-line prompt-line">
            <span class="prompt">&gt;_</span>
            <span class="executing">[EXECUTING]</span>
            <Cursor />
          </div>
        </div>
      </GlassCard>

      <!-- Testimonials -->
      <div class="testimonials">
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">
            "I'd paid two different agencies to rebuild our site over three years.
            Both times I ended up with something that looked fine but still didn't
            bring in clients. Spencer ran the diagnostic first, and it identified
            exactly why — our message was buried and there was no follow-up system.
            Six weeks later we had a site that generated 11 qualified leads in the
            first month. That had never happened before."
          </p>
          <footer class="testimonial-attr">
            — Marcus T., Owner, Commercial Cleaning Co., Richmond VA
          </footer>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">
            "I expected this to take two or three months. My site was live in eight
            days. More importantly, I actually understood what was built and why —
            I got documentation I could read, not a codebase I'd never open. We
            booked three new clients in the first two weeks from form submissions
            alone. I didn't even know the form was being used."
          </p>
          <footer class="testimonial-attr">
            — Priya S., Founder, HR Consulting Practice, Charlotte NC
          </footer>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">
            "I came to the diagnostic not knowing if I needed a new website, better
            software, or something else entirely. The questions forced me to think
            about my business differently — by the end I had a clearer picture of
            where I was losing people than I'd had in two years of running it. We
            ended up building a client intake app that replaced four separate tools.
            My team hasn't complained about our software once since it launched."
          </p>
          <footer class="testimonial-attr">
            — Daniel W., Managing Partner, Residential Property Mgmt, Raleigh NC
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section bottom rule -->
  <div class="section-bottom-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  /* Amber divider rule at top */
  .guide-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.15);
  }

  /* Section label — monospace, small, amber at 35% */
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Two-column grid */
  .guide-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5fr 4fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ── Empathy column ── */
  .empathy-opener {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .empathy-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: oklch(0.88 0.06 62);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .empathy-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ── Proof column ── */
  .proof-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  /* Authority terminal card */
  .terminal-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
  }

  .dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .dot.g {
    background: var(--success);
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--success);
  }

  .terminal-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .terminal-rule {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .status-list {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1;
  }

  .status-line {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-1) 0;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .status-badge {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .status-badge.ok {
    color: var(--success);
    text-shadow: 0 0 4px oklch(0.70 0.18 160 / 0.9), 0 0 8px oklch(0.70 0.18 160 / 0.35);
  }

  .status-text {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .status-value {
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: right;
  }

  .prompt-line {
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
    padding-top: var(--space-2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
  }

  .prompt {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .executing {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 4px oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.7);
  }

  /* ── Testimonials ── */
  .testimonials {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .testimonial {
    background: oklch(0.16 0.025 85);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--primary);
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-6) var(--space-6) var(--space-5);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm, 4px);
  }

  .testimonial-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: oklch(0.88 0.06 62);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .testimonial-attr {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ── Section bottom rule ── */
  .section-bottom-rule {
    height: 1px;
    background: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.20);
    margin-top: var(--space-20);
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .guide-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
    }

    /* Reorder: proof column first, empathy last */
    .proof-col {
      order: -1;
    }

    .empathy-col {
      order: 1;
    }
  }
</style>
